We've received your maintenance request and added it to the queue. You'll be notified once a vendor is assigned.

REQUEST DETAILS
---------------
Reference #: <%= request.mruid %>
Title:       <%= request.title %>
Category:    <%= request.category.replace(/_/g, ' ') %>
